This app was made for fun by [Derek Severson](https://github.com/derekseverson) to explore the possibilities of the Ionic Framework and practice AngularJS skills.

The source code and content of this app is open sourced on github. [Go take a look](https://github.com/derekseverson/AngularJS-StyleGuide-IonicApp).

This AngularJS Style Guide is a subcollection of the insightful AngularJS Style Guide by [@john_papa](http://twitter.com/john_papa) and other contributors.  John Papa's full version (not mobile) is located at this [github repo](https://github.com/johnpapa/angularjs-styleguide).
